### Test Calendar View
### Login first
POST http://localhost:3001/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@tiffin.com",
  "password": "demo123"
}

### Save accessToken from response

### 1. Get current month calendar (default)
GET http://localhost:3003/meals/calendar
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 2. Get specific month calendar (January 2024)
GET http://localhost:3003/meals/calendar?month=2024-01
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 3. Get specific month calendar (February 2024)
GET http://localhost:3003/meals/calendar?month=2024-02
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 4. Get specific week calendar (Week 3 of 2024)
GET http://localhost:3003/meals/calendar?week=2024-W03
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. Create some test meals first
POST http://localhost:3003/meals/bulk
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "startDate": "2024-01-15",
  "endDate": "2024-01-19",
  "skipWeekends": true,
  "mealType": "LUNCH",
  "count": 1
}

### 6. Add dinners
POST http://localhost:3003/meals/bulk
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "startDate": "2024-01-15",
  "endDate": "2024-01-19",
  "daysOfWeek": [1, 3, 5],
  "mealType": "DINNER",
  "count": 2
}

### 7. View calendar with all meals
GET http://localhost:3003/meals/calendar?month=2024-01
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
